task.summary:
Added right stick as throttle for arcade drive.
Also moved the OI-based arcade drive to the OI

Changes while testing 2/17/19:
- Added 2nd stick for throttle (up or down trims the speed to a max of 0.5) - Added HUD class and output from camera, roughed in output from arm position/aimer (once the sensor works)

Changes while drive testing 3/23/19:
- motors needed to be inverted on ball intake and drive - needed to remove motor trim
